            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_113wh' title='Col. 113WH &mdash; HC Deb 18 June 2003 vol 407 c113WH' name='column_113wh' href='#column_113wh' rel='bookmark'>113WH</a>
            should like to see a level playing field for the moneys that are raised here in the capital and with which we cross-subsidise the rest of the United Kingdom.
